data.title: Benito (name)
data.text:
BenitoPronunciationSpanish: [beˈnito]

Italian: [beˈniːto]GenderMaleOriginMeaning"blessed"Other namesRelated namesBenedetto, Benedict, Bento, Baruch, Mubarak

Benito is the Spanish form of Benedict and is both a masculine given name and a surname.[1] Notable people with the name include:
